new_generation

public boolean new_generation()
Run the all genetic algorithm phases, that are: 1.Calculate and set the values of the actual population; 2.In case maintain some best individuals (so a sorting will occur); define a new population by 3.Pick up two offspring with roulette selection; 4.Crossover these two offspring; 5.Mutate and add them to the new population;

Returns:
if the algorithms has performed correctly
